body:
i’m thankful for the famous people newsletter, the most recent issue of which is a breathless hungover ketchupy monologue that so perfectly distills being young and alive in the summer into the form of a party report: 

[https://famouspeople.substack.com/p/famous-people-43-ketchup-cupcakes?utm\_campaign=post&utm\_medium=web&utm\_source=copy](https://famouspeople.substack.com/p/famous-people-43-ketchup-cupcakes?utm_campaign=post&utm_medium=web&utm_source=copy)
